		<td colspan="2"><hr class="sep" />But that still leaves 1. when the address lines become valid, which affects the chip select going into the PPU, and 2. what value is held by bus capacitance before the write cycle begins. Perhaps in the STA $2004 case, the CPU isn't meeting the PPU's setup and hold requirement on some alignments.

		

		</td>
	</tr>
	</table>


